    "pinterest": "The ultimate romantic guide to Papua Paradise Eco Resort in Raja Ampat, Indonesia. Explore traditional overwater bungalows on Birie Island, pristine coral reefs, mandarin fish spotting, night snorkeling, and the iconic Pianemo viewpoint. Perfect for adventurous eco-luxury couples. #PapuaParadise #RajaAmpat #IndonesiaTravel #EcoResort #HoneymoonGuide #TravelCouples",
    "imageDescription": "A warm sunset photograph of traditional Papuan-style overwater bungalows on stilts at Papua Paradise Eco Resort in Raja Ampat, with the neon turquoise house reef visible below the wooden deck, and a hammock silhouetted against the golden evening sky.",
