    "imagePromptV2": "A realistic photograph of @image1 Male character and @image 2 female character snorkeling hand-in-hand above a shallow, vibrant coral reef in Raja Ampat, surrounded by tropical fish and clear turquoise water. Underwater photography style, natural daylight filtering through water, photorealistic, no text, no watermark.",
    "imagePromptV3": "A triptych collage of three naturally blended scenes: 1) the panoramic view of Raja Ampat's karst islands from the Pianemo hilltop viewpoint, 2) a close-up of a brilliantly colored mandarin fish on coral, 3) a traditional Papuan overwater bungalow at dusk. High realism, travel documentary style, photorealistic, no text, no border.",
    "imageSeoDetails": "Filename: papua-paradise-eco-resort-raja-ampat.jpg\nTitle: Papua Paradise Eco Resort, Raja Ampat: The Ultimate Romantic Island Guide\nAlt Text: Papua Paradise Eco Resort, Raja Ampat: The Ultimate Romantic Island Guide\nDescription: A warm sunset photograph of traditional Papuan-style overwater bungalows on stilts at Papua Paradise Eco Resort in Raja Ampat, with the neon turquoise house reef visible below the wooden deck, and a hammock silhouetted against the golden evening sky."
