      "Trofie al pesto at Osteria Tumelin, hand-pounded in Liguria's best basil. Sea kayaking along sea cliffs. A sea-view room with shuttered windows and the sound of waves. 🌿🛶 Levanto, we are not ready to leave. #LiguriaCuisine #PestoItaliano #BoutiqueItalyStay #TravelTogether #LuxuryTravelCouples"
