    "imagePromptV2": "A realistic photograph of @image1 Male character and @image 2 female character sitting in a rented golf cart on a scenic hillside road on Catalina Island, California, with the full panoramic view of Avalon Harbor and the Pacific Ocean below them. Bright California afternoon light, 50mm lens, photorealistic, no text, no watermark.",
    "imagePromptV3": "A triptych collage of three naturally blended scenes: 1) the iconic Avalon Casino Art Deco building at dawn reflected in the harbor, 2) a couple snorkeling in California's crystal-clear kelp forest with sunlight filtering through the fronds, 3) a table with fresh Pacific spiny lobster and white wine at a harbor-view restaurant. High realism, California travel editorial, photorealistic, no text, no border.",
    "imageSeoDetails": "Filename: boutique-stays-catalina-island.jpg\nTitle: Boutique Stays in Catalina Island: California's Most Romantic Island Escape\nAlt Text: Boutique Stays in Catalina Island: California's Most Romantic Island Escape\nDescription: A golden sunset photograph of Avalon Harbor in Catalina Island, California, showing the iconic circular 1929 Art Deco Casino building glowing in warm amber light reflected on the still harbor water, surrounded by colorful boats and hillside homes."
